rtility might be gonadotropins like hCG or FSH.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.049666,0.086081,0.091409,0.095908,0.097841,0.10067,0.095975,0.092277,0.0834,0.080719,0.067722,0.058333],"unified_progress":[0.080571,0.096692,0.1058,0.10162,0.097467,0.099934,0.088926,0.085963,0.075258,0.068553,0.055474,0.043739]},{"section":16,"text":"Putting this together: The key points are the ovarian cysts, very high estradiol, massive ascites, hypercoagulability (high hematocrit), and possibly hyperstimulation.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042784,0.081587,0.091328,0.094822,0.095241,0.094363,0.094284,0.090464,0.087298,0.083657,0.076241,0.067932],"unified_progress":[0.053971,0.081343,0.092042,0.097691,0.10056,0.098828,0.095414,0.089783,0.085613,0.079347,0.069477,0.055929]},{"section":17,"text":"The recent injection for infertility points to ovarian hyperstimulation syndrome (OHSS).","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036916,0.072404,0.083683,0.091614,0.095943,0.097614,0.097262,0.093229,0.089212,0.087796,0.07819,0.076136],"unified_progress":[0.048524,0.0695,0.081526,0.088655,0.092517,0.098172,0.094961,0.094309,0.091376,0.087576,0.080634,0.072249]},{"section":18,"text":"OHSS occurs after gonadotropin use, especially with hCG trigger.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035756,0.069266,0.080466,0.092091,0.10033,0.10342,0.10343,0.097233,0.088651,0.089161,0.073804,0.066391],"unified_progress":[0.048594,0.066195,0.083535,0.090175,0.095669,0.10514,0.10089,0.098857,0.092553,0.086689,0.072744,0.058953]},{"section":19,"text":"Symptoms include ovarian enlargement, ascites, pleural effusions (which could cause dyspnea), and in severe cases, renal impairment, thrombosis (high hematocrit suggests hemoconcentration?), but wait, hematocrit is elevated here.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030986,0.066265,0.078204,0.087195,0.094563,0